Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.99,0:00:27.30,Toptitle,,0,0,0,,If the sky clears, lalala we’ll sing
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.30,0:00:32.46,Toptitle,,0,0,0,,a song about our memories together
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.46,0:00:37.58,Toptitle,,0,0,0,,Surely if we’re apart our feelings will be connected
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.58,0:00:41.88,Toptitle,,0,0,0,,by a special magic
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.52,0:00:47.38,Toptitle,,0,0,0,,A memory from my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.38,0:00:52.82,Toptitle,,0,0,0,,overflowing me as I’m smiling and crying
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.82,0:00:57.70,Toptitle,,0,0,0,,Hiding my face from everybody
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.70,0:01:03.48,Toptitle,,0,0,0,,All of these treasured things
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.82,0:01:10.42,Toptitle,,0,0,0,,Beyond the horizon, a new road has begun
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.42,0:01:15.27,Toptitle,,0,0,0,,I want to take any wind towards it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.27,0:01:20.79,Toptitle,,0,0,0,,The important winds shining too for a second
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.79,0:01:25.64,Toptitle,,0,0,0,,All the while, it would be good to stay
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.64,0:01:28.92,Toptitle,,0,0,0,,Really, we grew a little,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.92,0:01:31.51,Toptitle,,0,0,0,,Had days that we were proud of
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.51,0:01:36.27,Toptitle,,0,0,0,,and days that we were nearly crying from laughter
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.27,0:01:41.87,Toptitle,,0,0,0,,All of these irreplaceable memories with friends
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.87,0:01:46.40,Toptitle,,0,0,0,,Let's hum an unending song
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.40,0:01:48.96,Toptitle,,0,0,0,,because we're a group
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.10,0:02:03.26,Toptitle,,0,0,0,,As we disappear together, a rainbow of happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.26,0:02:08.44,Toptitle,,0,0,0,,begins to form before us
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.44,0:02:13.59,Toptitle,,0,0,0,,Happy, fun, we meet all divided
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.59,0:02:17.88,Toptitle,,0,0,0,,in a good relationship
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.55,0:02:23.34,Toptitle,,0,0,0,,Talking casually,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.34,0:02:28.87,Toptitle,,0,0,0,,while blowing soap bubbles during an uncertain time
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.87,0:02:33.76,Toptitle,,0,0,0,,Still, I’m not scared
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.76,0:02:39.46,Toptitle,,0,0,0,,But now, I don’t want to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.84,0:02:46.38,Toptitle,,0,0,0,,Hold your head up high, with a blossoming smile
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.38,0:02:51.26,Toptitle,,0,0,0,,Try to look back on small moments like now
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.26,0:02:56.78,Toptitle,,0,0,0,,Let dream balloons float towards the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.78,0:03:01.62,Toptitle,,0,0,0,,Surely they will, here in this promised place
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.62,0:03:04.90,Toptitle,,0,0,0,,We liked the same things
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.90,0:03:07.40,Toptitle,,0,0,0,,We also had moments where we fought,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.40,0:03:12.38,Toptitle,,0,0,0,,only over little things
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.38,0:03:17.82,Toptitle,,0,0,0,,But we’re opening a new door together
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.82,0:03:22.44,Toptitle,,0,0,0,,talking about dreams that will come true
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.44,0:03:25.03,Toptitle,,0,0,0,,as a group
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.51,0:03:59.07,Toptitle,,0,0,0,,Beyond the horizon, a new road has begun
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.07,0:04:03.91,Toptitle,,0,0,0,,I want to take any wind towards it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.91,0:04:09.42,Toptitle,,0,0,0,,The important ones shining too for a second
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.42,0:04:14.28,Toptitle,,0,0,0,,All the while, it would be good to stay
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.28,0:04:17.48,Toptitle,,0,0,0,,We said “bye” and shook hands
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.48,0:04:20.15,Toptitle,,0,0,0,,We cried a bit
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.15,0:04:24.90,Toptitle,,0,0,0,,We can not go back through the door after this day
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.90,0:04:30.46,Toptitle,,0,0,0,,Surely some day from now on we will be shining
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.46,0:04:35.08,Toptitle,,0,0,0,,and we'll gather here and meet again
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.08,0:04:37.67,Toptitle,,0,0,0,,as a group
